race.comment: CYPHER PRINCE (4) just ran into one better before the spell and gets 1.5kg weight relief from the favourable draw. Tuned up for this with two recent trials and a strong showing while fresh would not surprise. MARAVICH (2) has had a few chances but the form he showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this calibre. Top-three aspirations. STILL UNWANTED (7) has placed two of his past three including one over this track and trip. Rock-hard fit and is right in the mix. DIVIL A BIT (1) is another to get some weight off and must be included from the low draw. Shouldn't be underestimated. ARTISTIC TOUCH (10) next best despite the outside draw.
